          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Using the various (Moscow (bremsstrahlung), Livermore",
                " and    Saclay    (quasimonoenergetic    annihilation",
                " photons))  experiments  data  for total photoneutron",
                " yield reaction  cross  sections  sig(g,xn)  and  the",
                " modern  model  of photonuclear reaction based on the",
                " Fermi gas densities equations the evaluated data for",
                " (g,n)   and  (g,2n)  reaction  cross  sections  were",
                " obtained for each individual experiments  and  after",
                " that  joint evaluations for both reactions have been",
                " done.",
                "Additionally joint  evaluation  has  been  done   for",
                " sig(g,xn)."
              ]
            }
          ],
